Package: byucorpora
Type: Package
Title: Search in Brigham Young University (BYU) Corpora
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Imports:
    curl,
    stringr,
    rvest,
    dplyr,
    tidyr
Authors@R: person("Earl", "Brown", email = "ekbrown77@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Earl Brown <ekbrown77@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions to webscrape the KWIC (keyword-in-context) display of
    the BYU corpora created by Mark Davies. The value returned by the various search
    functions is a data frame that can be saved to the hard drive and imported into
    a spreadsheet for analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
URL: https://github.com/ekbrown/byucorpora/
BugReports: https://github.com/ekbrown/byucorpora/issues/
